Revision history for Perl extension Schedule::Match.

0.01
 - Initial version.
 - This is a direct port of previous non-module version.

0.02
 - Added tests.
 - Incorporated better crash detection algorithm.
 - More documents.
 - Rewritten several parts for clarity.
 - Exports more methods.
 - Handles t_wm and t_om.
 - Fixed localtime for better compatibility.
 - Optimized some loop.

0.03
 - This is the first version to be upload to CPAN.
 - Changed module name to Schedule::Match (Time::Schedule was too generic).

0.04
 - Fixed a bug which caused "make test" to fail on some platform.
 - Minor documentation update.
